<< /DA (/CourierStd 10.00 Tf 0 g) /F 4 /FT /Tx /Ff 8388608 /MK << >> /P 17 0 R /Parent 27 0 R /Q 0 /Rect [ 427.499 671.19 594.0 689.825 ] /StructParent 3 /Subtype /Widget /T <feff00500031005f0044004f0042005f0046004c0044005b0030005d> /TU (Birthday \(M M/D D/Y Y Y Y\)) /Type /Annot >>
